    "Kaoru wiped the table and put the wet wipe back into her bag. A fan blew in the corner. The sign at the entrance said the air conditioner was broken.",
    "Yui set a drink down on the table. \"I got you a chu-hi,\" she said loudly, taking a cloth from her bag and wiping her forehead. \"It's really hot in here.\"",
