    "\"Kaoru, you made it,\" Takumi said. He pushed through the crowd and put a glass of chuhai on the table. \"What did you think?\"",
    "\"You were very good,\" Kaoru said. \"I loved your music.\"",
    "\"We have one more song to play, then we're going to sell some merchandise to the crowd,\" Takumi said. \"Can you help? Daichi is asking Yui.\"",
    "Kaoru bit her lip. \"I guess so,\" she said.",
